text: National Highway 844, commonly referred to as NH 844 is a national highway in India. It is a secondary route of National Highway 44. NH-844 runs in the state of Tamil Nadu in India. == Route == NH844 connects Hosur and Adiyamankottai, Dharmapuri in the state of Tamil Nadu. == Junctions == : Terminal near Hosur. : Terminal near Adiyamankottai,Dharmapuri == See also == * List of National Highways in India * List of National Highways in India by state == References == == External links == * NH 844 on OpenStreetMap Category:National highways in India Category:National Highways in Tamil Nadu
